mba is an exercise program that combines cardio muscle conditioning balance and flexibility.";i:5;s:114:"Each routine is made up of choreographed dance moves that combine elements of salsa reggaeton merengue and cumbia.";i:6;s:65:"Join me on August 25 2021 at 90000 AM EDT for a Zumba Gold class.";i:7;s:118:"2021-09-01T1630000000 2021-09-01T1730000000 utc Zumba Gold CHAIR with Leslie Leslie Sullins false YYYYMMDD Instructor.";i:8;s:34:"Leslie Sullins Additional Details.";i:9;s:77:"An exciting fitness concept that makes getting keeping fit enjoyable and fun.";i:10;s:134:"Even though you are getting an effective easy-to-follow workout Zumba Gold is more like a party with flamenco salsa tango belly dance.";i:11;s:43:"Using Zumba to make fitness more inclusive.";i:12;s:125:"Our Deputy Editor Shannon who uses a wheelchair didnt think she would be able to participate in able-bodied exercise classes.";i:13;s:71:"But she decided it was time to push boundaries by challenging the norm.";i:14;s:75:"So she and a fellow wheelchair user tried out a regular Zumba class at her.";i:15;s:104:"Oct 2 2021 - Explore Dawn Hamiltons board Zumba Gold Chair routines followed by 115 people on Pinterest.";i:16;s:53:"See more ideas about zumba gold chair senior fitness.";i:17;s:51:"People who want to get some serious core work done.";i:18;s:42:"Pull up a chair and tone your entire body.";i:19;s:119:"Zumba Sentao combines strength and resistance training with innovative dance moves using a chair as your dance partner.";i:20;s:130:"A high intensity workout that focuses on defining your muscles improving overall cardiovascular health and burning major calories.";i:21;s:34:"A Zumba class adapted for seniors.";i:22;s:90:"This class is all about taking care of our health in an atmosphere of celebration and joy.";i:23;s:114:"The emphasis is on cardiovascular improvement balance and muscle strength while maintaining safety for our joints.";i:24;s:261:"Taneční výuka belly dance orientální tanec břišní tanec Zumba fitness Latino dance Pole dance HOT HEELS tanec u tyče taneční škola ve Zlíně vystoupení a show taneční pobyty pravidelné taneční lekce lekce tance orient pro děti i seniory mix.";i:25;s:71:"And if a chair is used for this exercise the momentum doesnt slow down.";i:26;s:95:"The chair is used for high-energy aerobic dancing to help boost coordination and core strength.";i:27;s:104:"By using your body weight as resistance to tone muscles the chair becomes your true Zumba dance partner.";i:28;s:106:"This easy-to-replicate dance step mimics the movements of a Zumba class without requiring you to stand up.";i:29;s:13:"HOW TO DO IT.";i:30;s:97:"Sit on a the edge of a chair with your knees bent at 90-degree angles and your feet on the floor.";i:31;s:70:"Start by moving your right foot straight forward and tapping your toe.";i:32;s:50:"Take a seat get ready for a dance fitness workout.";i:33;s:84:"By utilizing a chair this Zumba class provides a low-impact option good for seniors.";i:34;s:103:"The class will feature seated movements that help to improve balance coordination and overall strength.";i:35;s:28:"Wheelchair Zumba with Katie.";i:36;s:18:"September 18 2020.";i:37;s:75:"Im a licensed Zumba instructor and I teach wheelchair Zumba online on Zoom.";i:38;s:79:"This class focuses on upper body movements including shoulders arms chest neck.";i:39;s:53:"Able body participants are more than welcome to join.";i:40;s:33:"Its a great workout for everyone.";i:41;s:20:"Its 8 per class and.";i:42;s:40:"Slow Dance of Love with Olga Danilevich.";i:43;s:173:"Enjoy the soothing lyrics and swaying movements of this beautiful and inspiring Chair Yoga Dance choreographed by Yoga for Seniors Teacher Olga Danilevich of Toronto Canada.";i:44;s:45:"This song will touch your heart and brighten.";i:45;s:31:"Chair Zumba Gold Fitness Class.";i:46;s:138:"Independent Living Community Chesapeake VA Chair Zumba Gold Fitness Classes invite all people to dance regardless of physical limita